text: Susanna Batazzi (born 29 August 1957) is an Italian fencer. She competed at the 1976 and 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Italy Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Fencers at the 1980 Summer Olympics
